\f2\b\fs28 \cf0 Project Goal\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa240\partightenfactor0

\f0\b0\fs24 \cf0 \
PrepAI aims to transform interview practice from a passive rehearsal into an active coaching session. We provide hyper-realistic AI interviewers and prescriptive, expert-level feedback to teach candidates how to craft and deliver compelling answers.\
\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa280\partightenfactor0

\f2\b\fs28 \cf0 Core Features (Phase 1)\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa240\partightenfactor0

\f0\b0\fs24 \cf0 \
This MVP focuses on delivering a single, high-value "Expert Assessment" report after a text-based mock interview.\
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\sa240\partightenfactor0
\ls2\ilvl0
\f2\b \cf0 \kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 \outl0\strokewidth0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
\outl0\strokewidth0 \strokec2 Dynamic Question Generation:
\f0\b0  Serves relevant questions based on the user's selected role and seniority.\
\ls2\ilvl0
\f2\b \kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 \outl0\strokewidth0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
\outl0\strokewidth0 \strokec2 Text-Based Interview Simulation:
\f0\b0  A clean chat interface for the user to practice answering questions.\
\ls2\ilvl0
\f2\b \kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 \outl0\strokewidth0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
\outl0\strokewidth0 \strokec2 Synchronous AI Analysis:
\f0\b0  Upon completion, the full interview transcript is sent to the Google Gemini API for a detailed performance review.\
\ls2\ilvl0
\f2\b \kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 \outl0\strokewidth0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
\outl0\strokewidth0 \strokec2 Structured Feedback Report:
\f0\b0  The AI returns a structured JSON report with a summary, scores, strengths, and areas for improvement.\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa240\partightenfactor0
