\f2\b\fs36 \cf0 2. System Architecture\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa240\partightenfactor0

\f0\b0\fs24 \cf0 \
The system is designed with a decoupled frontend and backend, communicating via a REST API. The analysis is performed synchronously for MVP simplicity.\
\
